  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">獵豹學子 林秉坤（八年級）</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">錄取清大物培/清大數培菁英班 心得分享</span></strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong><br />\n林秉坤同學</strong><br />\n參與 獵豹 高一輕競賽FS/高二數學課程S111/資優自然Sci系列<br />\n七年級考取：清大高中數學人才培育 菁英班<br />\n八年級考取：清大高中科學人才培育 物理組<br />\n八年級：2022 AMC12 117分<br />\n<br />\n<strong>秉坤同學心得：</strong><br />\n秉坤六年級參與獵豹高一數學輕競賽FS，七年級考取清大高中數學人才培育 菁英班，目前於高二S111，2022 AMC12: 117分。<br />\n<br />\n七年級參與Sci101/102國中資優化學/物理課程，課堂中老師講述深入又豐富，收穫良多，課程遠超過國中內容，讓秉坤在剛升上八年級就順利考上清大高中科學人才培育 物理組，能進一步和優秀的高中生們一起學習數理！也推薦給大家！</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\"><img src=\"pic/elite/cheetah-elite-41-body-1.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">『銜接高中化學最好的選擇：Sci12國中資優化學 Q&amp;A』<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1184525949166755/?__cft__[0]=AZVpzfMdIDOe6x7PFx2cpwevKYOikwRfWOE8yqc8KVel-4ON0YMhIz0Id8AXi3Dj9X8j1_ewBhs_9ZHYP-RzBhzMlTrz3w12O0hZbF3NKSl2b2c2dVcEKgujuNaDVpYt-NC8Oi1Zkd9qdXZA-1IQZoow&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../permalink/1184525949166755/</a><br />\n--<br />\n『S102、S112獵豹10高一、11高二資優數學網路課程(下)』<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1176967393255944/?__cft__[0]=AZVpzfMdIDOe6x7PFx2cpwevKYOikwRfWOE8yqc8KVel-4ON0YMhIz0Id8AXi3Dj9X8j1_ewBhs_9ZHYP-RzBhzMlTrz3w12O0hZbF3NKSl2b2c2dVcEKgujuNaDVpYt-NC8Oi1Zkd9qdXZA-1IQZoow&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/....../permalink/1176967393255944/</a></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1186740438945306/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1186740438945306/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
